    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab> (S.T.) In nomine domini Dei et salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Inperante
                        domno nostro <persName ref="#people/173" key="#Emperor/king">Otto</persName>
                        in Italia anno octavo et item <persName ref="#people/239"
                            key="#Emperor/king">Otto</persName> filio eius inperante idemque in
                        Italia anno secundo, meise iunio, indicione duodecima, acto <placeName
                            ref="#places/626" key="#Cities">Genua</placeName>. <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3902" key="#Churches #Monasteries"><rs
                                key="#Churches">Basilica</rs> Sancti Stefani</orgName> proto Christi
                        martiris, sita non longe a muro <rs key="#Cities">civitatis</rs> Ianua,
                        pertinente de sub regimine et potestate <rs key="#Bishops">episcopio</rs>
                        eiusdem sancte Ianuensis ecclesie, ubi <persName ref="#people/4648"
                            key="#Abbesses #marriage">Serra</persName>, Dei devota, veste religionis
                        induta et <rs key="#Abbesses">abatissa</rs> de adem basilica, ibidem Deo
                        servire videtur, ego quidem predicta Serra abatisa, donatrice et ofertris
                        ipsius basilice, p(resens) p(resentibus) dixi: quiquit in sancti ac
                        &lt;ven>erabilis locis et a suis aliquit contulerit rebus iusta Autoris
                        vocem in oc seculo centuplum accipiet et, quod melius est, vitam posidebit
                        eternam. Et ideo ego qui supra Serra abatisa, donatrice ipsius basilice,
                        dono, cedo, ofero per remedium et salutem anime <persName key="#marriage"
                                ><name ref="Marinus">Marini</name></persName>, <rs key="#marriage"
                            >qui fuit quondam vir meus</rs>, in eadem basilicam Sancti Stefani proto
                        Christi martiris i sunt omnibus rebus illis iuris mei proprietariis et
                        libellariis, quibus sunt sitis in locas et <rs key="#Fundi">fundas</rs>
                        <placeName key="Fundi"><geogName
                                key="#Petiae #Houses #Fundi #Forests #Cereals #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Chestnuts #Hay/fodder"
                                >Rivariole</geogName></placeName> et in <placeName key="Fundi"
                                ><geogName
                                    key="#Petiae #Houses #Fundi #Forests #Cereals #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Chestnuts #Hay/fodder"
                                >Mauriade</geogName></placeName> et in <placeName key="Fundi"
                                ><geogName
                                    key="#Petiae #Houses #Fundi #Forests #Cereals #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Chestnuts #Hay/fodder"
                                >Campofelegoso</geogName></placeName> et in <placeName key="Fundi"
                                ><geogName
                                    key="#Petiae #Houses #Fundi #Forests #Cereals #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Chestnuts #Hay/fodder"
                                >Cella seu Domoculta </geogName></placeName>et in <placeName
                            key="Fundi"><geogName
                                key="#Petiae #Houses #Fundi #Forests #Cereals #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Chestnuts #Hay/fodder"
                                >Granariolo</geogName></placeName> tam <rs key="#Houses">casis</rs>,
                            <rs key="#Wine">vineis</rs>, <rs key="#Chestnuts">castanetis</rs>,
                        canetis, <rs key="#Fruits/vegetables">salectis aliisque arboribus
                            fructiferis</rs>, <rs key="#Cereals">campis</rs>, <rs key="#Forests"
                            >silvis</rs> et <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pascuis</rs> ubicumque porcionem
                        vel sorte tam de proprietariis quam de libellariis inventa fuerit. Que mihi
                        qui supra Serra, Dei devota, unc die tenere et abere visa sum in
                        suprascriptis locis, una cum <rs key="#Canals">accepsionibus</rs> et
                        ingresoras earum seu cum superioribus et inferioribus earum in integrum ab
                        ac die in predicta basilica Sancti Stefani proto Christi martiri dono, cedo,
                        ofero per remedium anime predicti <persName key="#marriage"><name
                                ref="Marinus">Marini</name></persName>, qui fuit vir meus, et per
                        presentem cartam ofersioni ibidem abendum confirmo, faciendum exinde a
                        presenti die <rs key="#Abbots">abas</rs> predicte ecclesie sive subcessorum
                        suorum a pars predicte ecclesie proprietario iure quiquit voluerit, sine
                        omni mea qui supra Serra et eredum meorum contradicione de rebus
                        libellariis, salva quidem luminaria in sancta ecclesia, cuius est
                        proprietas, et liceat futurus aba uius eclesiae libellum petire a nomen suum
                        vel at subcessorum suorum. Quidem me espondeo a&lt;t>que promito ego qui
                        supra Serra, Dei devota, una cum meos eredes, suprascriptis casis et rebus
                        quiquit in predicta basilica oferte videor pars ipsius basilice ab omni
                        omine defen&lt;sar>e non potuerimus de rebus libellariis, preter de eclesia
                        cuius est proprie&lt;ta>s, aut super suprascriptis omnibus casis et rebus
                        exinde per covis ingenio subtraere quesierimus, tunc <rs key="#Penalty">in
                            duplum</rs> suprascriptis rebus a pars ipsius basilice restituamus sicut
                        pro tempore fuerint melioratis aut valuerit sub estimacione in consimilis
                        locis. Quam igitur cartam ofersionis me pagina <persName key="#Notary"><name
                                ref="Fulco">Fulcoinus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> scribendum rogavi, in qua subter confirmans
                        testi busque obtulit roborandum. Die regni et indicione suprascripta,
                        feliciter. Signum Serra abatisa, qui ac cartam oferscionis fieri rogavi.
                        Signum manibus <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Anselmus"
                            >Anselmi</name></persName> et <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Benedictus">Benedicti</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Angelrioco">Angelrioco</name></persName>,
                        rogati <rs key="#Witness">testes</rs>. (S.T.) <persName key="#Judge"><name
                                ref="Alexander">Alexamder</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> rogatus subscripsi. (S.T.) <persName
                            key="#Judge"><name ref="Thomas">Thomas</name></persName> iudex rogatus
                        subscripsi. (S.T.) <persName key="#Judge"><name ref="Silveradus"
                                >Silveradus</name></persName> iudex subscripsi. (S.T.) <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Andreas">Andrea</name></persName> iudex
                        rogatus subscripsi. <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Teodero"
                                >Teodero</name></persName> rogatus subscripsi. <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Gotefredus">Gotefredus</name></persName>
                        rogatus subscripsi. (S.T.) Ego qui supra Fulcoinus not&lt;arius> scribsi et
                        subscripsi, complevi et dedi.</ab>
                </div>
